name: Princess Royalty Coat
description:
The quilted nylon shell and soft fleece lining of the Princess coat give your pup protection and warmth. Faux fur pom poms and plush neck trim add contrasting details, and a heart-shape design overlaid on a crown adorns the royal garment. Made of machine-washable polyester.

description:

name: Pinkaholic Sprinkles Flirt Pink
description:
The Pinkaholic Sprinkles Flirt harness is made out of 100% Cotton. It is a harness and dress all-in-one. It has a polka dot and stripe scheme so your little lady pup can be flirty and stylish all at the same time. This easy on-and-off harness has Velcro closure around the neck and under the trunk. Along the back is a stacked Double D-ring for safety and comfort.
